# Interesting LTL formulas used during development of aut2ltl.

# basic — reconstructed cleanly
(p U q) & GF r
FG a
a U b
G (p -> X p) & GF q
G(Xp2 & (p0 | Xp1))   # exercises downstream invariants + t2 + precise SCC attachment

# f2-required — needs the size-2 fusion heuristic
X(p1 | F(p1 & Xp1))

# problematic — very-weak / release shapes
!p1 W p0
G!p2 R p1
